window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>As Father Magnus Falke, I suppress my cravings. As the headteacher of a Catholic boarding school, I’m never tempted by a student. Until her…</b></p> <p>I became a priest to control my impulses.</p> <p>Then I meet Tinsley Constantine.</p> <p>The bratty princess challenges my rules and awakens my dark nature. With each punishment I lash upon her, I want more. In my classroom, private rectory, and bent over my altar, I want all of her. There’s no absolution for the things I’ve done.</p> <p>One touch risks everything I stand for. My faith. My redemption. And even my life.</p> <p>As if that could stop me. I need her pain, and her heart, and she needs my lessons in sin.</p>"; 
